sentences: Yukari Tamura (田村 ゆかり, Tamura Yukari, born February 27, 1976) is a Japanese voice actress and singer affiliated with Amuleto (formerly Arts Vision and I'm Enterprise).
She debuted as a voice actress in 1997, releasing her debut single "Yūki o Kudasai" on March 26, 1997.
In 2001, Tamura formed a unit called Yamato Nadeshiko alongside Yui Horie.
In February 2016, Tamura's agency announced that a concert which had been announced during a Niconico livestream in 2015 would be cancelled.
On February 13, 2016, her management announced that her contract with King Records would end on March 20, 2016.
